text: Wasna Ahmed is an Indian television actress. She made her debut with the role of Dhara in Kasautii Zindagii Kay. She also played titular character in Shree. ==Filmography== ;Films *2013 Kadhal Solla Aasai (Tamil) as Suchitra *2015 Palaandu Vaazhga ;Television *Kasautii Zindagii Kay as Dhara *Kahe Naa Kahe as Kinjal (opposite Karan Hukku) *Shree as Shree *Kabhi Kabhii Pyaar Kabhi Kabhii Yaar as herself *Dance India Dance as herself *Aahat as Rani *C.I.D.
